OPENID Plugin
==============

This is the OPENID plugin for Tuleap. It provides:
- OpenID authentication support for users for web access only.

See the Tuleap User Guide for more informations.

Installation
-------------
1. Install the tuleap-plugin-openid RPM
2. Make sure that it is the 'codendi' auth which is set in /etc/codendi/conf/local.inc for the '$sys_auth_type' variable
